They enjoy all the songs of suffering

01:06:08.720 --> 01:06:11.520
and then they become themselves tragic.

01:06:11.720 --> 01:06:14.520
Such people cannot give joy to anyone.

01:06:14.720 --> 01:06:16.440
I mean people run away

01:06:16.640 --> 01:06:19.960
from such people. They think he is a person who is a mourner.

