If somebody dies and has no mourners they can be paid.

01:06:26.640 --> 01:06:28.640
And they are brought for crying and weeping

01:06:28.840 --> 01:06:30.360
and saying all these things you see

01:06:30.560 --> 01:06:32.600
there are people paid for it in India. Imagine.

01:06:32.800 --> 01:06:35.120
I mean we use them for  this purpose.

01:06:35.320 --> 01:06:37.960
Artificially they can mourn somebody's death

01:06:38.160 --> 01:06:40.400
and earn some money out of it.

01:06:40.600 --> 01:06:44.600
But such kind of miserable people

01:06:45.080 --> 01:06:47.640
are such a

01:06:47.840 --> 01:06:49.840
blot on the name of God

01:06:50.040 --> 01:06:52.440
who has given you so much.

01:06:52.640 --> 01:06:55.720
Count your blessings.

01:06:55.920 --> 01:06:59.280
Count your blessings one by one.

01:06:59.480 --> 01:07:01.480
First of all that

01:07:01.680 --> 01:07:06.080
you are not under the control of the nature, the parsha.

01:07:06.280 --> 01:07:10.080
You are a free human being.

01:07:10.280 --> 01:07:12.080
So many things He has given you

01:07:12.280 --> 01:07:14.280
and still you are weeping and crying

01:07:14.480 --> 01:07:18.000
and saying that we have to suffer.

01:07:18.200 --> 01:07:20.560
who believe in suffering will get it.

01:07:20.760 --> 01:07:23.480
You want suffering? Then have it.

01:07:23.680 --> 01:07:25.480
They get it.

01:07:25.680 --> 01:07:30.720
And these people can really go so much with it

01:07:30.920 --> 01:07:32.560
about the suffering part

01:07:32.760 --> 01:07:38.960
that recently I met one group in Spain.

01:07:40.120 --> 01:07:42.120
And I said, "What are you doing about your seeking?"

01:07:42.320 --> 01:07:44.160
They said, "We are going to Gobi Desert."

01:07:44.360 --> 01:07:45.560
I said, "For what?"

01:07:45.760 --> 01:07:47.200
"There's the Shambhala is there."

01:07:47.400 --> 01:07:48.760
I said, "What is that Shambhala?"

01:07:48.960 --> 01:07:52.160
"It's the God's heaven in Gobi Desert. And there's a gentleman

01:07:52.360 --> 01:07:53.920
who is going to take us to the Gobi Desert

01:07:54.120 --> 01:07:56.640
and we are going to walk in the center of Gobi Desert."

01:07:56.840 --> 01:07:57.720
I said, "Very nice."

01:07:57.920 --> 01:08:00.360
"And we are paying so much money for that."

01:08:00.560 --> 01:08:02.040
Now in that Gobi desert

01:08:02.240 --> 01:08:06.640
you can't get even a drop of water.

01:08:06.840 --> 01:08:07.880
You pay lot of money

01:08:08.080 --> 01:08:09.640
to go to that Gobi Desert,

01:08:09.840 --> 01:08:11.600
walk across, and die there.

01:08:11.800 --> 01:08:14.760
And this man gets all the money you know befooling [HERE?].

01:08:14.960 --> 01:08:16.480
"But then we must suffer."

01:08:16.680 --> 01:08:18.520
For what?

01:08:18.720 --> 01:08:21.720
Why you want to suffer?

01:08:21.920 --> 01:08:25.160
Christ has suffered for you enough.

01:08:25.360 --> 01:08:27.280
If Christ is awakened within you

01:08:27.480 --> 01:08:30.520
He will take up everything upon Himself.

01:08:30.720 --> 01:08:33.360
He'll really wash all your sins

01:08:33.560 --> 01:08:35.680
and you can get your realization.

01:08:35.880 --> 01:08:38.120
That's how it works so quick.

01:08:38.320 --> 01:08:41.160
If you know how to enlightened Him within yourself

01:08:41.360 --> 01:08:42.920
then it works out.

01:08:43.120 --> 01:08:46.400
Still the Christians are even continuing with ideas

01:08:46.600 --> 01:08:47.760
leave alone the Jews.

01:08:47.960 --> 01:08:51.600
Christians are just the same.

01:08:52.640 --> 01:08:56.480
And they enjoy you see this kind of suffering upon themselves.

01:08:56.680 --> 01:08:58.840
Is all imaginary.

01:08:59.040 --> 01:09:03.560
Like we went to France in Paris.

01:09:03.760 --> 01:09:06.960
"We are all miserable people le miserable."

01:09:07.200 --> 01:09:08.320
And they told Me,

01:09:08.520 --> 01:09:10.520
"Don't tell them Mother that you are happy, you know.

01:09:10.720 --> 01:09:11.800
They'll not like it.

01:09:12.000 --> 01:09:13.960
You better tell that you are the most miserable."

01:09:14.200 --> 01:09:16.040
Le miserable.

01:09:16.240 --> 01:09:19.600
All miserables sitting there.

01:09:19.800 --> 01:09:21.960
I said, "What miserable they are."

01:09:22.160 --> 01:09:25.760
Every third lamppost you'll find a pub

01:09:25.960 --> 01:09:29.480
and every seventh lamppost you'll find a prostitute.

01:09:29.680 --> 01:09:31.960
This is the miserable thing they have.

01:09:32.160 --> 01:09:36.640
Do miserable people do all these things?

01:09:36.800 --> 01:09:39.400
Just sitting outside for the last doomsday,

01:09:39.640 --> 01:09:41.800
the calamity. They'll have it

01:09:42.000 --> 01:09:44.400
if they want to have it.

01:09:44.600 --> 01:09:47.320
But God has not created you to be miserable at all.

01:09:47.520 --> 01:09:48.720
No, not at all.

01:09:48.920 --> 01:09:53.400
He has created you to be very happy and joyous

01:09:53.600 --> 01:09:58.440
to enjoy the beauties of His bounties.

01:09:58.640 --> 01:10:00.720
We are really letting Him down

01:10:00.920 --> 01:10:03.400
and it's really such a miserable thing. Supposing now

01:10:03.600 --> 01:10:05.400
you want to invite somebody to your house.

01:10:05.600 --> 01:10:08.600
Your own son is coming. You are so excited about him.

01:10:08.800 --> 01:10:11.800
You are so anxious that your son after such a long time

01:10:12.000 --> 01:10:13.480
such a long journey

01:10:13.680 --> 01:10:16.200
is coming as a glorious man to your house

01:10:16.400 --> 01:10:21.560
and then he's weeping saying, "I'm miserable."

01:10:22.840 --> 01:10:26.080
So those people who indulge into the left side of the Swadhisthana

01:10:26.280 --> 01:10:27.880
so much

01:10:29.760 --> 01:10:30.960
suffer

01:10:31.160 --> 01:10:33.880
because they enter into an area called

01:10:34.080 --> 01:10:35.600
collective subconscious

01:10:35.800 --> 01:10:39.200
and this is the area which the other day doctors pointed out.

01:10:39.400 --> 01:10:41.960
they were studied the cancer disease they said

01:10:42.200 --> 01:10:46.760
a vulnerable person who is vulnerable to cancer

01:10:46.960 --> 01:10:49.120
the one who's an extreme temperament person.

01:10:49.320 --> 01:10:52.440
A person who is extremely hard working can be vulnerable also.

01:10:52.640 --> 01:10:57.880
But is triggered, is triggered by

01:10:58.080 --> 01:11:02.440
a protein which they call as protein 58

01:11:02.640 --> 01:11:05.760
or protein 52

01:11:05.960 --> 01:11:08.320
which enters into the being,

01:11:08.520 --> 01:11:12.360
which triggers it, and this protein one

01:11:12.560 --> 01:11:15.440
is coming from the area called as

01:11:15.640 --> 01:11:17.480
according to them we call it

01:11:17.680 --> 01:11:20.080
collective conscious. Collective subconscious.

01:11:20.280 --> 01:11:26.200
But they call it the area built in within us since the creation.

01:11:26.440 --> 01:11:31.200
I mean they say something else. We make it clearer that's all.

01:11:31.400 --> 01:11:34.120
And cancer is caused by that.

01:11:34.320 --> 01:11:38.720
Invariably I have seen those people who have come to Me from cancer

01:11:38.920 --> 01:11:41.560
have been the people who got it from left side.

01:11:41.760 --> 01:11:47.640
You wanted to suffer? All right have cancer. Enjoy it.

01:11:48.600 --> 01:11:51.800
But there was a journalist who came to see Me in America

01:11:52.000 --> 01:11:55.960
and I told him that you should not suffer.

01:11:56.160 --> 01:11:59.080
So he folded everything. He said, "I'm going back".

01:11:59.280 --> 01:12:01.920
He said, "It is my right to suffer."

01:12:02.120 --> 01:12:05.080
Imagine. I said, "Now what to say to this man?"

01:12:05.280 --> 01:12:07.560
I said, "All right then go ahead with it.

01:12:07.800 --> 01:12:09.800
When you are fed up with it you come to Me.

01:12:10.000 --> 01:12:13.680
But just now you have a right to suffer. Do what you like."

01:12:13.880 --> 01:12:17.120
If somebody wants to hit himself

01:12:17.320 --> 01:12:19.880
with a bamboo or something

01:12:20.080 --> 01:12:21.320
and you say, "Why do you want to hit yourself?"

01:12:21.520 --> 01:12:23.200
Say, "It's a right, my right to hit myself."

01:12:23.400 --> 01:12:27.000
I said, "All right hit." But you have no right

01:12:27.200 --> 01:12:30.200
because you cannot create yourself.

01:12:30.400 --> 01:12:32.920
You have no right to torture yourself.

01:12:33.120 --> 01:12:36.120
You have no right to make yourself miserable.

01:12:36.320 --> 01:12:39.320
You have to make yourself happy people,

01:12:39.520 --> 01:12:40.960
joyous people,

01:12:41.160 --> 01:12:45.160
blissful people so that God feels

01:12:45.360 --> 01:12:48.120
you have received blessings.

01:12:48.320 --> 01:12:50.280
That He may be placed

01:12:50.480 --> 01:12:56.240
through His own creation that is the epitome, the human beings.

01:12:56.440 --> 01:13:00.080
That's the best way you should please God by saying,

01:13:00.280 --> 01:13:02.760
"Father we are very happy people.

01:13:02.960 --> 01:13:07.200
Don't worry about us. We are so thankful to You."

01:13:08.000 --> 01:13:10.800
So that's how the joy killers come to us from the left side.

01:13:10.960 --> 01:13:14.320
The right side is the people who kill others' joy.

01:13:14.520 --> 01:13:18.800
Spoil sports as you call them in a very mild way.

01:13:18.960 --> 01:13:20.960
They are the ones who are aggressive.

01:13:21.160 --> 01:13:24.200
They cannot see anybody being peaceful.

01:13:24.400 --> 01:13:26.760
Even countries can be like that.

01:13:26.960 --> 01:13:28.440
Collectively they can do like this.

01:13:28.640 --> 01:13:31.600
If they see any country is peaceful, they'll attack.

01:13:31.800 --> 01:13:34.360
"Why is he peaceful?

01:13:34.560 --> 01:13:37.640
We must attack and capture that country."

01:13:37.840 --> 01:13:44.040
The people who cannot bear the joy of other people

01:13:44.440 --> 01:13:48.360
become aggressive and try to aggress them.

01:13:48.560 --> 01:13:54.760
There are people who just get sometimes jealous.

01:13:55.240 --> 01:14:00.440
Sometimes just for aggression they become aggressive.

01:14:00.640 --> 01:14:01.920
I have no reason sometimes

01:14:02.120 --> 01:14:05.120
the way people suddenly shoot up like Jack in the Box

01:14:05.320 --> 01:14:07.960
and start talking in such an aggressive manner

01:14:08.200 --> 01:14:10.640
you don't understand why should we aggress.

01:14:10.880 --> 01:14:13.280
is no need to aggress at all.

01:14:13.480 --> 01:14:15.320
But they go on aggressing people.

01:14:15.520 --> 01:14:16.600
Then they may form

01:14:16.800 --> 01:14:19.080
a thing like as a German state

01:14:19.280 --> 01:14:22.840
that we are a superior race, a sense of superiority.

01:14:23.040 --> 01:14:29.960
All your racialism comes from this nonsense of a aggression.

01:14:32.480 --> 01:14:35.120
I mean I can't understand Western people.

01:14:35.320 --> 01:14:39.280
For example they're so particular about their race being preserved

01:14:39.480 --> 01:14:41.600
because they think they are white skin.

01:14:41.800 --> 01:14:45.200
But they go to the sea, make it black. Why?

01:14:45.400 --> 01:14:49.240
I mean either you are white skin or you have black. One of the two.

01:14:49.440 --> 01:14:51.320
So they are so confused.

01:14:51.520 --> 01:14:52.960
They think they are not beautiful

01:14:53.200 --> 01:14:55.840
because they are white skin, light skin.

01:14:56.040 --> 01:14:56.960
So if you are not so beautiful

01:14:57.200 --> 01:15:00.440
then why do you think you are above the world?

01:15:00.640 --> 01:15:03.680
Racialism is something so much

01:15:03.880 --> 01:15:06.760
a mental projection, absolutely a mental projection

01:15:06.960 --> 01:15:12.360
and with this mental projection we gather so much of

01:15:12.560 --> 01:15:16.920
curses of [THE OTHER WORLD?].

01:15:17.120 --> 01:15:20.320
I'll give you an example. We went to China.

01:15:20.520 --> 01:15:23.680
And Chinese are so much against British I was surprised.

01:15:23.880 --> 01:15:26.280
So much against. The worst are British according to them.

01:15:26.480 --> 01:15:27.920
They had seven aggressors.

01:15:28.120 --> 01:15:30.520
I said, "Why?"

01:15:30.720 --> 01:15:32.960
Because they gave them dopes you see.

01:15:33.160 --> 01:15:35.600
And if you ask the British of that time they will say that,

01:15:35.800 --> 01:15:36.840
"Because they deserved it.

01:15:37.040 --> 01:15:41.880
We gave them. See, what's wrong?"

01:15:42.080 --> 01:15:44.560
But when I told them that

01:15:44.760 --> 01:15:47.240
Britishers are taking drugs and all that. "Nice for them.

01:15:47.440 --> 01:15:49.080
Let them all take it.

01:15:49.280 --> 01:15:52.240
That's what they deserve.

01:15:52.440 --> 01:15:56.920
They're drunkards. Let them have the drugs."

01:15:57.120 --> 01:15:59.600
Nobody will have the sympathy with people who are aggressors.

01:15:59.800 --> 01:16:02.120
If you think you are a great [RACE?], go ahead with it.

01:16:02.320 --> 01:16:06.480
And the more [RACE?] is going toward the doom.

01:16:06.680 --> 01:16:10.240
You must know you must learn from others also.

01:16:10.440 --> 01:16:12.920
People have learned from you politics, economics.

01:16:13.120 --> 01:16:14.560
I don't know what you've made out of it.

01:16:14.760 --> 01:16:16.320
If you think you have done very good, well,

01:16:16.520 --> 01:16:18.080
I have nothing to say.

01:16:18.280 --> 01:16:19.840
Also other things they have learned from you.

01:16:20.040 --> 01:16:23.240
English language I have learned.

01:16:24.480 --> 01:16:27.840
And why do you call everybody a lower

01:16:28.040 --> 01:16:29.800
developed thing? You are a developed country.

01:16:30.000 --> 01:16:31.160
What have you developed?

01:16:31.360 --> 01:16:33.840
Atom bombs to kill yourself?

01:16:34.040 --> 01:16:35.880
What have you developed?

01:16:36.080 --> 01:16:37.760
All kinds of aggressiveness.

01:16:37.960 --> 01:16:40.440
You go to other country with a Bible in the hand and another

01:16:40.640 --> 01:16:45.440
a pistol in the your hand or a rifle in your hand to kill others.

01:16:45.720 --> 01:16:48.440
This aggression comes from mental projection that we have

01:16:48.640 --> 01:16:52.120
that we are great you see puffed up.

01:16:52.320 --> 01:16:55.600
The best for that is Humpty Dumpty sat on a wall.

01:16:55.800 --> 01:16:57.000
That's the one it is.

01:16:57.200 --> 01:16:58.760
Is that the Humpty Dumpty's.

01:16:58.960 --> 01:17:01.400
I tell you all [RIGHTS? HEIGHTS?].

01:17:01.600 --> 01:17:04.120
All [RIGHTS? HEIGHTS?] are so sensible.

01:17:04.320 --> 01:17:06.560
And they said the Humpty Dumpty sat on a wall

01:17:06.760 --> 01:17:08.720
and Humpty Dumpty had a big fall.

01:17:08.920 --> 01:17:12.880
And all the king's horses and men could not put them together again.

01:17:13.080 --> 01:17:16.040
That's what it is a Humpty Dumpty a big ego like a balloon.

01:17:16.240 --> 01:17:18.360
They'll float like as if something

01:17:18.560 --> 01:17:20.280
you see like angels in the world

01:17:20.480 --> 01:17:21.720
while when they'll reach

01:17:21.920 --> 01:17:24.880
the kingdom of God, God will say, "What business you had to hate

01:17:25.080 --> 01:17:29.040
any part of this creation.

01:17:29.240 --> 01:17:30.720
Who are you I don't know."

01:17:30.920 --> 01:17:34.040
Because in collectivity you are so poor in this respect.

01:17:34.240 --> 01:17:35.680
So we have to understand

01:17:35.880 --> 01:17:37.880
that God has created all of us.

01:17:38.080 --> 01:17:40.360
We have to have variety.

01:17:40.560 --> 01:17:42.200
It looks nice

01:17:42.400 --> 01:17:44.640
that you wear another dress. I wear another dress.

01:17:44.840 --> 01:17:46.840
I have another face. You have another face.

01:17:47.040 --> 01:17:50.960
Unless and until there are variety in the nature

