01:55:58.480 --> 01:56:01.640
Bring your lunch along.

01:56:01.840 --> 01:56:03.480
It should be a good day.

01:56:03.680 --> 01:56:07.080
Tomorrow evening Mother will speak about the Heart Chakra,

01:56:07.280 --> 01:56:09.960
the center of security within us.

01:56:10.200 --> 01:56:12.320
The Vishuddhi Chakra which is the center

01:56:12.520 --> 01:56:15.760
in which we are able to witness the drama of life

01:56:15.960 --> 01:56:17.760
and get our self esteem.

01:56:17.960 --> 01:56:22.200
And the Agnya Chakra which is the center of Christ which relates to

01:56:22.400 --> 01:56:24.520
the principle of the Spirit,

01:56:24.720 --> 01:56:26.800
the quality of forgiveness.

01:56:26.960 --> 01:56:31.160
And then finally the Sahasrara Chakra which is the center

01:56:31.360 --> 01:56:36.120
which Mataji Herself has opened in this incarnation.

01:56:36.320 --> 01:56:41.640
So the two successive lectures are going to deal with those centers.

01:56:41.800 --> 01:56:44.360
